summary: A test suite that verifies the Stable Diffusion inpainting pipeline using an asymmetric KL autoencoder across multiple configurations, including model download, compilation, various samplers (DDIM, K‑LMS, PNDM), precision modes (fp16), input resolutions, strength settings, and sequential CPU offloading.
business_intent: Validate the correctness, stability, and performance of the inpainting pipeline before release, preventing regressions and ensuring compatibility with different hardware and runtime options.
